    public class DriveKinectWaypointLeft
extends DriveWaypoint
    If the Kinect arms are to the left, execute the DriveWaypoint command, otherwise return quickly. The DriveWaypoint command will drive the robot forwards to a waypoint on the field based on its original starting position.
